text.tspan: On the global market, there is an increase in the demand for marble. Rapid
growth in the construction industry in several developing regions across the
world is likely to propel the demand further.
It is expected a 3% increase from 2016 to 2020. Worldwide market growth at a
CAGR of 11,5% over the next five years is expected, and within 2023 it will reach
21 billion US$, from 12,2 billion US$ in 2017. Within this period, it is especially
the white marble that is under the highest demand.
